================================================================================
THIRD-PARTY RESOURCES AND ATTRIBUTIONS
================================================================================

This application uses the following third-party resources:

1. PEXELS API
   - Provider: Pexels (https://www.pexels.com)
   - License: Pexels License (https://www.pexels.com/license/)
   - Usage: All photos provided through Pexels API
   - Free for commercial and non-commercial use
   - Attribution not required but appreciated
   - Photos cannot be sold as-is or in a database
   - Note: This application displays photos from Pexels for user selection and editing

2. BUNNY FONTS
   - Provider: Bunny Fonts (https://fonts.bunny.net)
   - License: Open Font License (OFL) and various open source licenses
   - Usage: Web font delivery service
   - Free to use for personal and commercial projects
   - Privacy-focused alternative to Google Fonts
   - Includes fonts like: Abeezee, Abril Fatface, Acme, Aladin, Amatic SC, 
     Audiowide, Bangers, Berkshire Swash, Cinzel, Damion, Great Vibes, 
     IBM Plex Sans Arabic, Noto Kufi Arabic, and many more

3. COLOR HUNT
   - Provider: Color Hunt (https://colorhunt.co)
   - License: Free to use color palettes
   - Usage: Color palette inspiration and selection
   - Free for personal and commercial use
   - Colors used in this application are inspired by Color Hunt palettes
   - No copyright restrictions on individual colors

4. GOOGLE MATERIAL ICONS
   - Provider: Google (https://fonts.google.com/icons)
   - License: Apache License 2.0
   - Usage: User interface icons
   - Free for personal and commercial use
   - Available at: https://github.com/google/material-design-icons

