IMPORTANT LEGAL NOTICES
================================================================================

IMAGE USAGE NOTICE:
- All images displayed in this application are sourced from Pexels API
- Images are subject to Pexels License terms
- Users are responsible for ensuring proper usage of images they edit/download
- This application does not claim ownership of any images from Pexels
- Images are provided "as is" for editing purposes only

FONT USAGE NOTICE:
- All fonts are loaded from Bunny Fonts CDN
- Fonts are subject to their respective open source licenses
- Most fonts use the SIL Open Font License (OFL)
- This application does not redistribute font files
- Fonts are loaded dynamically from Bunny Fonts servers

COLOR USAGE NOTICE:
- Color palettes are inspired by Color Hunt
- Individual colors are not copyrightable
- Color combinations are provided for design inspiration
- No trademark or copyright infringement is intended

NO DATA COLLECTION:
- This application does not collect, store, or transmit user data
- All image editing happens locally in the browser
- No images or edits are uploaded to any server (except Pexels API for browsing)
- User preferences (theme, language) are stored locally using localStorage

